  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The usual ship of the line of most modestly-funded frontier navies -- a true warship, albeit minimal in size. Good armor, multiple ship-killing guns, and trained boarding marines make a corvette a death sentence to most stellar ruffians. Its cargo lighter allows crew and cargo transit to worlds it cannot land on, and its extended stores allow more than four months of field operation.</p><p><strong>Crew:</strong> 10/40. <strong>Cost:</strong> 5.973M base price, 298,650cr six-month maintenance, 1.314M yearly crew cost (30 crew).</p>",
